Package com.jme3.bullet.animation

Class RangeOfMotion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme3.bullet.animation.RangeOfMotion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jme3.export.Savable
    public class RangeOfMotion
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.jme3.export.Savable
    A range-of-motion preset for a ragdoll joint. Immutable except for read(com.jme3.export.JmeImporter).
